<h1>Jingxiao Cai's Blog</h1>
<p>Technical blog by Jingxiao Cai about ML infrastructure, distributed systems, self-hosted AI agents, debugging, automation, and production engineering.</p>
<p class="search-box"><a href="{{ site.basePath }}search.html">Search this static archive</a> · <a href="{{ site.basePath }}feed.xml">RSS Feed</a></p>
<p class="prototype-note">Eleventy prototype: Markdown posts generated from the current static HTML, Nunjucks layouts for shared metadata, fixed <code>.html</code> permalinks, and Pagefind indexing after build.</p>
<h2>Blog Posts</h2>
{% for post in collections.posts %}
<div class="post">
  <h3><a href="{{ site.basePath }}{{ post.data.slug }}.html">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h3>
  <p class="date">{{ post.data.date | dateDisplay }}{% if post.data.updated %} · Updated {{ post.data.updated | dateDisplay }}{% endif %}</p>
  {% if post.data.tags and post.data.tags.length %}<p class="categories">Categories: {{ post.data.tags | join(', ') }}</p>{% endif %}
  <p>{{ post.data.summary or post.data.description }}</p>
</div>
{% endfor %}
<hr>
